// =============================================================================
// core/database/sqlite/native/test_vectors/mod.vr
// =============================================================================
// Layer: 7+ (test infrastructure)
// Spec: sqlite-native.md Appendix E
//
// Codified file-format test vectors. Each table is a `List<…>` of
// (input, expected) pairs the test runners feed into the relevant
// L0 / L2 component:
//
//   * `varint`         — Appendix E.1 — 38 representative pairs
//                         spanning every length class 1-9 bytes
//   * `record_encoding`— Appendix E.2 — record-header parses
//   * `wal_checksum`   — Appendix E.3 — fnv-1a-shaped frame checksums
//   * `btree_cell`     — Appendix E.4 — interior + leaf + index cells
//
// The full Appendix E vector set (128 + 50 + 20 + 50) lives in
// `vcs/conformance/sqlite/vectors/`. The tables here are the
// load-bearing subset that exercises every code path; CI loads the
// full set via the runner.
// =============================================================================

module core.database.sqlite.native.test_vectors;

public module varint;
public module record_encoding;
public module wal_checksum;
public module btree_cell;
